com.foreach.across.modules.entity.autosuggest

Class EntityQueryAutoSuggestData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.entity.autosuggest.EntityQueryAutoSuggestData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoSuggestDataSet, AutoSuggestDataSet.ResultTransformer

    public class EntityQueryAutoSuggestData
extends Object
implements AutoSuggestDataSet, AutoSuggestDataSet.ResultTransformer
    Represents auto-suggest data for a registered entity. Data is fetched using an EntityQuery and transformed using the EntityModel.

    The queries to be executed can be specified using either a supplier of the EntityQuery instance or simply as EQL statement. The EQL statement can hold a \{0\} token where the actual search string will be inserted.

    Since:
    3.4.0
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
